     1	# Relay Agent Assistant
     2	
     3	Shared open-source assistant SDK/runtime for AgentWorkforce products such as Sage, MSD, NightCTO, and future assistants.
     4	
     5	## What This Repo Is
     6	
     7	This repository defines the shared assistant layer that sits above Relay foundation infrastructure and below product-specific assistants.
     8	
     9	It exists to centralize assistant concerns that should not be reimplemented in every product:
    10	
    11	- assistant identity and runtime composition
    12	- memory contracts and shared retrieval/persistence patterns
    13	- session continuity across surfaces
    14	- proactive behavior and scheduled follow-up engines
    15	- multi-agent coordination behind one assistant identity
    16	- policy, approvals, and audit hooks
    17	
    18	## Current Status
    19	
    20	**6 packages implemented and passing tests. 4 packages are placeholder/README-only. 1 package (traits) is planned for v1.2.**
    21	
    22	Implementation vs specification status at a glance:
    23	
    24	| Package | Implementation | Spec | Tests | Notes |
    25	| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
    26	| `@relay-assistant/core` | **IMPLEMENTED** | `SPEC_RECONCILED` | 31 pass | matches `v1-core-spec.md` |
    27	| `@relay-assistant/sessions` | **IMPLEMENTED** | `IMPLEMENTATION_READY` | 25 pass | matches `v1-sessions-spec.md` |
    28	| `@relay-assistant/surfaces` | **IMPLEMENTED** | `SPEC_RECONCILED` | 28 pass | matches `v1-surfaces-spec.md` |
    29	| `@relay-assistant/routing` | **IMPLEMENTED** (DoD gap) | `IMPLEMENTATION_READY` | 12 pass | test count below 40+ DoD target — **do not consume in products until resolved** |
    30	| `@relay-assistant/connectivity` | **IMPLEMENTED** | `IMPLEMENTATION_READY` | 30 pass | matches `v1-connectivity-spec.md` |
    31	| `@relay-assistant/coordination` | **IMPLEMENTED** | `IMPLEMENTATION_READY` | 39 pass | routing integration reviewed; escalation pipeline dormant (v1 known gap) |
    32	| `@relay-assistant/memory` | **placeholder** | `IMPLEMENTATION_READY` | — | spec exists at `docs/specs/v1-memory-spec.md`; roadmap: v1.1 |
    33	| `@relay-assistant/policy` | **placeholder** | none | — | no formal spec yet; roadmap: v2 |
    34	| `@relay-assistant/proactive` | **placeholder** | none | — | no formal spec yet; roadmap: v1.2 |
    35	| `@relay-assistant/examples` | **placeholder** | N/A | — | reference examples; not production code |
    36	| `@relay-assistant/traits` | **planned — v1.2** | none | — | assistant identity traits, voice, style, behavioral defaults — see [traits and persona layer](docs/architecture/traits-and-persona-layer.md) |
    37	
    38	**Total implemented: 165 tests, all passing.**
