    51	## Traits and Persona Context
    52	
    53	Products using this SDK should understand the distinction between workforce personas and assistant traits before writing product adapter code.
    54	
    55	**Workforce personas** are runtime execution profiles (model, harness, system prompt, service tier). These are defined and owned in Workforce infrastructure. They are not imported from this SDK.
    56	
    57	**Assistant traits** are identity and behavioral characteristics (voice, style, vocabulary, proactivity level). The `@relay-assistant/traits` package is planned for v1.2. In v1, products define traits as local data objects and inject them manually into persona prompts and format hooks.
    58	
    59	See [traits-and-persona-layer.md](../architecture/traits-and-persona-layer.md) for the full boundary definition.
