   147	
   148	**What stays in Sage for now:**
   149	- Knowledge and workspace-specific prompt behavior
   150	- Workforce persona definitions (model, harness, system prompt, tier) — these are workforce-owned, not SDK concerns
   151	- Product-specific follow-up heuristics
   152	- Slack-specific UI conventions and block kit templates
   153	- Trait values (voice, style, vocabulary) — define as a local data object; `@relay-assistant/traits` ships at v1.2
